{"tid":524702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屋企隻貓一樣咁廢鳩","createTime":"2018-01-10T00:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T03:41:02.000Z","uid":28007,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be4f634f1957c8a9623eb53f179ed70cd35202e9","tid":524702,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:17:29.000Z","msg":"近排天氣開始轉涼<br />\n我屋企條廢青既生活模式都轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時佢已經有個暖笠笠既竇<br />\n依家仲要加埋個暖爐比佢佢先肯入去訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/080640_d8ec236dd7dcc10a6444826ef729afa0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F080640_d8ec236dd7dcc10a6444826ef729afa0.png&h=3bf0d680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日會做既野由食訓屙 變成訓醒 坐係暖爐隔離暖陣 之後食同屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/080826_775672978ba34911a9cc4c66c30e6d2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F080826_775672978ba34911a9cc4c66c30e6d2a.png&h=841d237a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔理個爐有無開 總之坐左係隔離先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說琴日番完工好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番到屋企頂唔順想訓個靚教<br />\n咁就搬個暖爐入房訓 然後佢就跟埋入黎嘈住我訓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/081129_c053fc2b1bc9a6e3ca43d66d22d47f51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F081129_c053fc2b1bc9a6e3ca43d66d22d47f51.png&h=845cc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係諗唔明 點解一隻貓可以廢到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生左咁多毛但係要霸住個暖爐用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻貓陪左我十幾年 已經係老貓一隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日係佢生日 望住佢愈黎愈老 我好怕佢離開我既𠴱一日黎臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢貓可否不要老 以後都嘈住我訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a06a538a199a4dabbc8b3fbd2ed19334b3c03d","tid":524702,"uid":49918,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b8dac4571a6c879b39c30f8a5b3362bfcf6551f","tid":524702,"uid":98018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:20:38.000Z","msg":"老貓係咁㗎喇 食到瞓到仲想點 對得一日賺一日"},{"pid":"556d2cd18b00f443b9f1d0831fdfbcbba46f6504","tid":524702,"uid":13724,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:23:20.000Z","msg":"有無發覺樓主不繼借意影自己隻腳"},{"pid":"36b3387dec9d578b557b2a5b8d53da3ce0881c7e","tid":524702,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f5cf5263d5473fe6e64f6d85c43fee22221796","tid":524702,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無發覺樓主不斷借意影自己隻腳</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a05c8688e2886873a87a1a5ab77764d7a2da96d3","tid":524702,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:24:58.000Z","msg":"你都識話佢係老貓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7692186a7418dca94c333db48bc5474e64b1db1b","tid":524702,"uid":119993,"like":0,"dislik